item.title: The hell?
item.dc:creator: @error.login cane
item.description:
@error.login wrote:

[quote=“Aeolian, post:76, topic:323448”][quote author=Cole1497 link=topic=419831.msg3469890#msg3469890 date=1295210970]

My real number is 100 and something.

When kaitnieks.com closed down, he linked to a website that RaW (an “infamous scammer”) was running to sell a new version of auto_rune. It didn’t take long for most people to know that it was just another scam, and the members there were mostly old TARC assholes and we weren’t very welcome. Members from kaitnieks then went to 1 of 2 places, moparisthebest.com/smf or saradomin.net

I went to saradomin.net first, so I was a little late at joining the mitb forums. Saradomin.net was ran by abyssal, who was a big name in the scar scripting community. But he was very young and didn’t have much experience running websites, so it turned into a failure pretty soon. Eventually everyone flocked to moparisthebest.com

I can’t recall why, but something happened to these forums and they needed to be reset from scratch. I was on IRC while mopar was doing this, so I was the 4th member after the reset. It’s fun to reminisce about those days.
[/quote]I love reminiscing about the old days. Ahhh such good times. I miss 'em <3

You have 2 posts from 2006, and the rest are 2010 and 2011.

You do realize that there was a massive prune back in the day and people lost hundreds of posts. Hence why all of mine aren’t from 06’ HURR DURR.[/quote]
cool story bro

Read full topic
